aws organization:
 -account management service enables you to consolidate multiple aws accounts into an organization tht you create and centrally ,maanage
Tips:
-limit 20 linked accounts for consolidated billing
Available in two feature sets:
-consolidate billing
-all features

root -(policy)-> ou --> aws account
     -(policy)-> ou --> aws account
     -(policy)-> aws account
     
Eg:
  paying account(independent acnnot access other accounts)-->Test
                                                          -->Dev     > all will have same monthly bill 
                                                          -->prod 
                                                          
advantages:
-one bill per aws account
-very easy to track charges and alocate costs
-volume pricing discount

Best practices
- enable multifactor auth for root acc
